  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWhen downloading a nethermind release from github and extracting the zip file the working directory is filled with many files/directories because the zip files content is located in the zip's root and not a subfolder.\r\n\r\n```\r\n% wget -qO ~/download/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2.zip https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/releases/download/1.13.2/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2-795dd1e-20220607.zip\r\n% unzip -q ~/download/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2.zip\r\n% ls -l\r\ntotal 345040\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 Data\r\n-rw-r--r-- 1 mm mm      7695 Jun  7 10:34 NLog.config\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm 114156800 Jun  7 10:39 Nethermind.Cli\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm  50071455 Jun  7 10:39 Nethermind.Launcher\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm 189053078 Jun  7 10:37 Nethermind.Runner\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 chainspec\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 configs\r\n-rw-r--r-- 1 mm mm        20 Jun  7 10:36 git-hash\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 keystore\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:37 plugins\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nBest practice in software development and software distribution is to put all the archive content in a single subfolder with that subfolder being named after the software with the version appended.\r\n\r\n```\r\n% wget -qO ~/download/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2.zip https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/releases/download/1.13.2/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2-795dd1e-20220607.zip\r\n% unzip -q ~/download/nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2.zip\r\n% ls -l\r\ntotal 4\r\ndrwxrwxr-x 7 mm mm 4096 Jun  8 12:52 nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2\r\n% ls -l nethermind-linux-amd64-1.13.2/\r\ntotal 345040\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 Data\r\n-rw-r--r-- 1 mm mm      7695 Jun  7 10:34 NLog.config\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm 114156800 Jun  7 10:39 Nethermind.Cli\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm  50071455 Jun  7 10:39 Nethermind.Launcher\r\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 mm mm 189053078 Jun  7 10:37 Nethermind.Runner\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 chainspec\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 configs\r\n-rw-r--r-- 1 mm mm        20 Jun  7 10:36 git-hash\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:38 keystore\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 mm mm      4096 Jun  7 10:37 plugins\r\n```",
